posting_body: ['This is an recently remodeled in-law apartment in Sunset District.', "It's on 1st floor with 2 bedroom,1 bathroom,1 combined living room/dining room/Kitchen area.", 'Washer and Dryer is available, the place is nice and comfortable with fresh air and good sunlight.', 'The entrance to the in-law is independent from the main entrance of the house.', "It's close to a commercial street (Irving ST, Lincoln way and the Golden gate park)", "It's conveniently close to transportation and grocery shopping, muni train to downtown is N Judah and other muni buses to other areas close by.", "It's suitable for singles.", 'preferably students or young professionals.', 'No parties and no pets please.', 'Rent is $2300 available in NOW', 'If interested, please email me with a short resume about yourself.']
